// Semantic direction:
// spill_semantikk models computation as a game between Player (the program) and Opponent (context/environment).
// arena defines the moves and their enabling relationships — who can move after whom.
// spørsmål_trekk initiates a subcomputation; svar_trekk answers a pending question.
// enablement_relasjon: trekk m enables m' if m' can only be made after m.
// strategi is a deterministic function from positions to moves — it models a program's behavior.
// interaksjon composes two strategies σ:A→B and τ:B→C to produce τ∘σ:A→C.
// innocent_strategi: σ's move depends only on the view (the subsequence of odd-indexed moves).
// AJM_semantikk (Abramsky-Jagadeesan-Malacaria) proved full abstraction for PCF.
// ajm_well_bracketed: questions and answers are properly nested (stack discipline).
// hyland_ong gives an alternative full abstraction proof using hereditarily innocent strategies.
// geometri_of_interaction models cut-elimination as token passing in a proof net.
// goi_operator represents a proof as a partial isometry on a Hilbert space.
// cbpv_spill extends game semantics to Call-by-Push-Value, cleanly separating values from computations.
// stateful_spill adds store locations and read/write moves for modeling mutable state.
// full_abstraksjon_spill: two programs are denotationally equal iff no game-context distinguishes them.
// may_testing: e₁ ≤_may e₂ if every context that makes e₁ converge also makes e₂ converge.
// must_testing: e₁ ≤_must e₂ if every context that makes e₂ diverge also makes e₁ diverge.

// Primitive flow:
// PCF term f: int→int modelleres som spill:
//   Opponent åpner med spørsmål q (forespørsel om verdien av f)
//   Player svarer (kanskje etter å ha stilt spørsmål til argument)
//   Svar danner en interaksjons-sekvens: q · q' · a' · a
// Komposisjon av strategier σ: A→B og τ: B→C:
//   kjør σ og τ parallelt, skjul B-trekk (interaksjon)
//   resultat: strategi over A og C-trekk alene
// Innocent sjekk: σ(s·a) = σ(s'·a) når s og s' har lik view
//   -> σ trenger bare huske hva som hentes fra argument, ikke hele historikk
// Full abstraksjon: PCF denotasjon = klassen av innocent, well-bracketed, deterministic strategier

// This defines game semantics: arenas with enabling, Player/Opponent strategies, composition,
// innocent strategies with views, the AJM and Hyland-Ong full abstraction theorems for PCF,
// geometry of interaction, CBPV game semantics, games for effects (state/exceptions/probability),
// and may/must testing orderings.
